    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/294040/extras/SteamImage08.JPG?t=1770745359\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一条传说中的恶龙正在八方肆虐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城镇燃起了熊熊烈火，它还用魔法复活了世间的邪恶生灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此时急需一位英雄，去往世界各地，手刃怪兽，恢复和平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RPG 刷刷刷盛宴！开跑，战胜越来越强的敌人，积攒经验和战利品，购买更好的装备，提升等级，然后再来一次！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一大波不同的敌人和头目</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量不同的装备升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包括放置元素，即使不在线，你的矿工也会收集金币</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走心的复古画风</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁各种成就</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成怪物图鉴</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集卡片</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持手柄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大概是无尽玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多到惊人的战利品和经验！ <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/294040/extras/fbe0603db75bdbfff6a04fc0dac21fe5.avif?t=1770745359\" width=618 height=256 /></span></p></li></ul>",
